'''哈罗德·雷米斯'''（{{lang-en|Harold Allen Ramis}}，{{bd|1944年|11月21日|2014年|2月24日|catIdx=Ramis}}）是一名[[犹太|犹太]]血统的美国男演員、喜剧演员、导演和編劇<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.algemeiner.com/2014/02/24/‘ghostbusters’-actor-‘caddyshack’-director-harold-ramis-dies-at-69/|title=‘Ghostbusters’ Actor, ‘Caddyshack’ Director Harold Ramis Dies at 69|work=Algemeiner Journal|date=February 24, 2014|accessdate=April 24, 2018|archive-date=2020-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820204557/https://www.algemeiner.com/2014/02/24/%E2%80%98ghostbusters%E2%80%99-actor-%E2%80%98caddyshack%E2%80%99-director-harold-ramis-dies-at-69/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Ethan|last=Sacks|url=http://beta.nydailynews.com/entertainment/actor-harold-ramis-dead-69-article-1.1699957|title=Harold Ramis dead at 69: Actor-director-writer was best remembered for ‘Ghostbusters,’ ‘Groundhog Day’|work=New York Daily News|date=February 24, 2014|accessdate=April 24, 2018}}{{Dead link}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Perry|last=Garfinkel|url=https://www.lionsroar.com/harold-ramis-profile-by-perry-garfinkel/|title=Harold Ramis didn’t intend “Groundhog Day” to be Buddhist, but it’s a dharma classic|work=Lion's Roar magazine|date=February 2, 2018|accessdate=April 24, 2018|archive-date=2018-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180221203041/https://www.lionsroar.com/harold-ramis-profile-by-perry-garfinkel/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Robert|last=Loerzel|url=http://www.chicagomag.com/arts-culture/February-2014/Harold-Ramis-Q-A/|title=11 Questions for Harold Ramis: An Unpublished Interview|work=Chicago magazine|date=April 24, 2014|accessdate=April 24, 2018|archive-date=2018-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180424202512/http://www.chicagomag.com/arts-culture/February-2014/Harold-Ramis-Q-A/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他最著名的作品包括《{{link-en|条纹布 (电影)|Stripes (film)|条纹布}}》（1981年）中的羅素和《[[捉鬼敢死队|捉鬼敢死队]]》（1984年）中的[[伊根·史賓格勒|伊根·史賓格勒]]，而他也是两部电影编剧。雷米斯影響了後代的喜劇演員和創作者，如[[傑·洛奇|傑·洛奇]]、[[傑克·卡斯丹|傑克·卡斯丹]]、[[亞當·山德勒|亞當·山德勒]]和[[法拉利兄弟|法拉利兄弟]]都喜愛引用他的電影。

2014年，雷米斯因自體免疫感染血管炎的综合症，死于家中，享年69岁<ref>{{Cite web|title=Harold Ramis, Chicago actor, writer and director, dead at 69|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/chi-harold-ramis-dead-20140224,0,2259309.story|first=Mark|last=Caro|publisher=''[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]]''|date=February 24, 2014|accessdate=February 24, 2014|archive-date=2014-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140719025022/http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/chi-harold-ramis-dead-20140224,0,2259309.story|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

